sequenceDiagram
    participant LocalClient as "Cursor IDE"
    participant NPMPkg as "@verygoodplugins/mcp-automem"
    participant FlaskAPI as "Flask API :8001"
    participant MCPBridge as "mcp-sse-server :8080"
    participant CloudClient as "ChatGPT"
    participant DB as "FalkorDB/Qdrant"

    Note over LocalClient,DB: Local MCP Flow (stdio)
    LocalClient->>NPMPkg: MCP request via stdio
    NPMPkg->>FlaskAPI: POST /memory<br/>Authorization: Bearer TOKEN
    FlaskAPI->>DB: Store memory
    DB-->>FlaskAPI: Success
    FlaskAPI-->>NPMPkg: 201 Created
    NPMPkg-->>LocalClient: MCP response

    Note over LocalClient,DB: Cloud MCP Flow (Streamable HTTP)
    CloudClient->>MCPBridge: POST /mcp<br/>tool: store_memory<br/>?api_token=TOKEN
    MCPBridge->>MCPBridge: Extract token<br/>getAuthToken(req)
    MCPBridge->>FlaskAPI: POST /memory<br/>Authorization: Bearer TOKEN
    FlaskAPI->>DB: Store memory
    DB-->>FlaskAPI: Success
    FlaskAPI-->>MCPBridge: 201 Created
    MCPBridge-->>CloudClient: JSON-RPC response

    Note over LocalClient,DB: Direct HTTP Flow
    LocalClient->>FlaskAPI: POST /memory<br/>Authorization: Bearer TOKEN
    FlaskAPI->>DB: Store memory
    DB-->>FlaskAPI: Success
    FlaskAPI-->>LocalClient: 201 Created